### Alerts

#### POST /alerts

Ingests an alert from an external monitoring tool (e.g. Datadog, Prometheus, Grafana).

```json
{
  "source": "datadog",
  "title": "High error rate on payment-service",
  "severity": "P1",
  "service": "payment-service",
  "details": { "error_rate": "37%", "threshold": "5%" }
}
```

