## Rate Limiting

| Tier | Limit | Window |
|------|-------|--------|
| Standard | 1,000 requests | Per minute |
| Enterprise | 10,000 requests | Per minute |

Rate limit headers are included on every response:

```http
X-RateLimit-Limit: 1000
X-RateLimit-Remaining: 982
X-RateLimit-Reset: 1710647040
```

